    <h2 class="annotation">Annotation</h2>
    <div class="annotation">
        <div class="annotation-body annotation-collapse">
                <p>Italian baroque composer, violinist and organist</p>

        </div>

        <div class="annotation-details">
            
                Annotation last modified on 2012-01-09 23:40 UTC.
            
        </div>
    </div>
    
<h2 class="wikipedia">Wikipedia</h2>
<div class="wikipedia-extract-body wikipedia-extract-collapse"><p><b>Giovanni Battista Draghi</b> (<small>Italian pronunciation: </small><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)">[dʒoˈvanni batˈtista ˈdraːɡi]</span>; 4 January 1710 – 16 March 1736), best known as <b>Pergolesi</b> (<small>Italian: </small><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)">[perɡoˈleːzi]</span>) or <b>Giovanni Battista Pergolesi</b>, was an Italian composer, violinist and organist.</p>
<p></p></div>
<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Giovanni_Battista_Pergolesi">Continue reading at Wikipedia...</a>
